<lg n="65" type="stanza">
<l n="322">Oh reader! now that I might tell </l>
<l n="323">What Johnny and his horse are doing! </l>
<l n="324">What they&rsquo;ve been doing all this time, </l>
<l n="325">Oh could I put it into rhyme, </l>
<l n="326">A most delightful tale pursuing! </l>
