<pb>
<milestone unit="page" n="171">
<lb>
<lb>
<lg n="66" type="stanza">
<l n="327">Perhaps, and no unlikely thought! </l>
<l n="328">He with his pony now doth roam </l>
<l n="329">The cliffs and peaks so high that are, </l>
<l n="330">To lay his hands upon a star, </l>
<l n="331">And in his pocket bring it home. </l>
