<lg n="68" type="stanza">
<l n="337">And now, perhaps, he&rsquo;s hunting sheep, </l>
<l n="338">A fierce and dreadful hunter he! </l>
<l n="339">Yon valley, that&rsquo;s so trim and green, </l>
<l n="340">In five months&rsquo; time, should he be seen, </l>
<l n="341">A desart wilderness will be. </l>
