<lb>
<lb>
<lg n="69" type="stanza">
<l n="342">Perhaps, with head and heels on fire, </l>
<l n="343">And like the very soul of evil, </l>
<l n="344">He&rsquo;s galloping away, away, </l>
<l n="345">And so he&rsquo;ll gallop on for aye, </l>
<l n="346">The bane of all that dread the devil. </l>
