<lg n="82" type="stanza">
<l n="407">&ldquo;Oh! Johnny, never mind the Doctor; </l>
<l n="408">&ldquo;You&rsquo;ve done your best, and that is all.&rdquo; </l>
<l n="409">She took the reins, when this was said, </l>
