<lb>
<lg n="87" type="stanza">
<l n="432">&ldquo;Alas! what is become of them? </l>
<l n="433">&ldquo;These fears can never be endured, </l>
<l n="434">&ldquo;I&rsquo;ll to the wood.&rdquo;&mdash;The word scarce said,</l>
<l n="435">Did Susan rise up from her bed, </l>
