<lg n="88" type="stanza">
<l n="437">Away she posts up hill and down,</l>
<l n="438">And to the wood at length is come, </l>
<l n="439">She spies her friends, she shouts a greeting;</l>
<l n="440">Oh me! it is a merry meeting, </l>
